Some exploratory Analysis

Regression Models

So far we’ve created four regression models * Initial model with all variables: modelfit1 * LASSO model * Forward selection model using p-values as criteria: modelfoward * Backward selection model using p-values as criteria: modelbackward * Stepwise selection model using p-values as criteria: modelstepwise
